### 3.5 Transfer of Intellectual Property Rights upon Compensation

If the Author offers compensation for a specific Contribution and **the Contributor
expressly accepts such offer in writing**, then upon receipt of compensation that is
fair and reasonable in relation to the market value of the Contribution at the time of
transfer, all intellectual property rights in that specific Contribution are
